<Base title="Author" description="Greg Simpson">
  <section class="section page-shell">
    <h1>About Greg Simpson</h1>
    <p>
      Greg Simpson is the author of <em>The Quantum Contingent</em> and <em>Quantum Time</em>. He writes adventure and
      mystery novels weaving technology and science with real world intrigue.
    </p>
    <p>
      Greg retired in March 2021, after a 37-year career in technology. He spent 20 years in healthcare IT as a CIO,
      CTO, and Chief Technology and AI leader for a Fortune 200 healthcare company.
    </p>
    <p>
      Greg lives in Colorado with his wife, Karen, and they have two adult children. He blogs about both the locations
      and technology in his books.
    </p>
    <p>
      In 2026, he continues work on the series and ongoing research for future stories.
    </p>

